Module 8 RAG Corpus — License Notice
=====================================

The corpus in `data/corpus.jsonl`, together with the labeled evaluation sets
in `data/retrieval_eval.jsonl` and `data/rag_eval.jsonl`, is a derivative work
based on:

1. The BEIR CQADupStack benchmark
   - https://huggingface.co/datasets/BeIR/cqadupstack
   - https://huggingface.co/datasets/BeIR/cqadupstack-qrels
   - License: Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International
     (CC BY-SA 4.0)

2. The public Stack Exchange data dump (April 2024 snapshot)
   - https://archive.org/details/stackexchange
   - Subsets used: softwareengineering.stackexchange.com (the former
     programmers.stackexchange.com), webmasters.stackexchange.com,
     android.stackexchange.com.
   - Underlying user content on the Stack Exchange Network is licensed by its
     authors under Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International
     (CC BY-SA 4.0); historical posts may be CC BY-SA 3.0. We treat the
     entire corpus as CC BY-SA 4.0 for downstream use.

Because both upstream sources are CC BY-SA, this derivative corpus is also
distributed under CC BY-SA 4.0:

   https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

Per the ShareAlike obligation, any redistribution or adaptation of this corpus
must:
  (a) attribute the original Stack Exchange authors and the Stack Exchange
      Network (see ATTRIBUTION.md for the canonical attribution text);
  (b) attribute the BEIR benchmark and its maintainers (see ATTRIBUTION.md);
  (c) be itself distributed under CC BY-SA 4.0 or a compatible license.

Build scripts in `scripts/` and configuration files in this directory are not
derivative of the corpus content and are released under the terms of the
parent `aispire-14005` repository.
